{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-log-post-jsx","path":"/themes-with-css-variables/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Here’s a CSS variable (formally called a “CSS custom property“):</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">:root</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">--mouse-x</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">--mouse-y</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Perhaps you use them to set a position:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.mover</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--mouse-x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--mouse-y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>To update those values from JavaScript, you’d:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\">let root = document.documentElement<span class=\"token selector\">;\n\nroot.addEventListener(\"mousemove\", e =></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  root.style.<span class=\"token function\">setProperty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'--mouse-x'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> e.clientX + <span class=\"token string\">\"px\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  root.style.<span class=\"token function\">setProperty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'--mouse-y'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> e.clientY + <span class=\"token string\">\"px\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Set theme with global css variables","date":"2021-01-12","tags":["css","theme","style"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/themes-with-css-variables/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}